    public class DetailsFragment
extends android.support.v4.app.Fragment
    A simple Fragment subclass. Activities that contain this fragment must implement the DetailsFragment.OnFragmentInteractionListener interface to handle interaction events. Use the newInstance(java.lang.String, java.lang.String) factory method to create an instance of this fragment.
